          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By author - the experiments are performed by measuring",
                "the elastic scattering yields near the coulomb barrier",
                "energies for the 32-S(12-C,12-C)32-S,",
                "32-S(14-N,14-N)32-S, and 32-S(16-O,16-O)32-S reactions.",
                "Direct scattering of the lighter ions was measured",
                "because the high 32-S ion energies needed could not be",
                "achieved, and therefore, the cross sections were",
                "calculated from the kinematically reversed",
                "12-C(32-S,12-C)32-S, 14-N(32-S,14-N)32-S, and",
                "16-O(32-S,16-O)32-S reactions.",
                "The uncertainties in the cross section values,",
                "resulting from the statistical and background",
                "subtraction errors in the determination of the peak",
                "areas, increased from 2% at the low energy end to 5%",
                "towards the  high  energy  end of the given ion energy",
                "intervals.  A small error may be introduced in the",
                "cross sections due to the natural isotopic abundance of",
                "sulfur (95% 32-S) in the Zn-S target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REL-REF": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "N",
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": "M.BOZOIAN",
                "reference": {
