              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Experimental and theoretical non-Rutherford",
                "threshold energies for elastic scattering"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A Zn-S sample was used for cross section measurements",
                "and a manganese sample was chosen for background",
                "subtraction. The Zn-S and Mn films thicknesses 40 and",
                "55 mu-gramm/cmm**2, respectively. The films were",
                "fabricated by the e-gun vacuum evaporation technique on",
                "carbon foils on temporary glass  supports.  The films",
                "were furher coated by thin gold film with 54",
                "mu-gramms/cm**2 for ion dose normalization purposes.",
                "The gold film was to serve as an internal dose",
                "reference."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The interference from the reaction yields produced by",
                "the carbon substrate were eliminated by subtracting the",
                "normalized manganese spectra from the Zn-S spectra.",
                "The Mn film thickness was chosen to correspond to",
                "average energy loss of the differentions in the Zn-S",
                "film."
              ]
            }
          ],
